-- Former England Star Michael Owen To Retire At End of the Season
-- B y   D a n i e l l e   R o s s i n g h
-- 2013-03-19T09:46:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-03-19/former-england-star-michael-owen-to-retire-at-end-of-the-season.html
Former England and Liverpool player
 Michael Owen  said he’ll retire from soccer at the end of the
season.  “It is with an immense amount of pride that I am
announcing my intention to retire from professional football,”
Owen, 33, said in a statement on his website.  Having made his debut for Liverpool at the age of 17, Owen
represented England in 89 matches. He currently plays for Stoke
City.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Danielle Rossingh in London at 
